 of tools to progress the story and defeat enemies.<br>    -A full set of rings with effects you can unlock.<br>    -Map of the game that unlocks as you progress.<br>    -Upgrade system for weapon and tools.<br>    -Side quests for NPCs with their own side story.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622110/extras/3a8d7c89d7af34a64432e5f5d679a8cb.poster.avif?t=1764733266\" width=428 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622110/extras/3a8d7c89d7af34a64432e5f5d679a8cb.webm?t=1764733266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622110/extras/3a8d7c89d7af34a64432e5f5d679a8cb.mp4?t=1764733266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
